string.value: Aufheben splits the sky with a blinding light.

string.name: msg
string.value: After destruction comes judgment. With the party's thesis and antithesis debuffs out of balance, a random party member will be KO'd.

string.value: Ashray's will has temporarily suppressed Aufheben.

string.name: msg
string.value: The force of destruction is accelerating. If you don't pair up with another party member who has a different thesis debuff from you, you'll be KO'd in 10 seconds.
